<body>
<div1 type="summary">
<p>Order for medicine.</p>
</div1>

<div1 type="body">

<p><person_mentioned>Mr Moses Austin</person_mentioned></p>
<p>Dear Sir</p>

<p>You'l be as kind as to [send] me, one viol of that
Medicine which was in the same; I have be taken with the Rumitis
in one of my 'Leggs' that I am not able to walk a bout</p>

<p>[Peter Love.]</p>
<p><location_mentioned>Mine A Burton</location_mentioned> <date_mentioned n="03-20-1811">20th March 1811</date_mentioned></p>
</div1>
